posts.post_title: Ca. 1900 Bob Wicker Cabinet & Fan Craze Card (Last Reduction)
posts.post_content:
I have for your consideration a circa 1900 Bob Wicker Cabinet Photo along with his Fan Craze Card. The Cabinet has St. Louis superimposed over his Dayton Jersey. He played for Dayton in 1900 and played for St. Louis starting in 1901. This cabinet was probally used for St. Louis Team Composite. Cabinet is 3"w. by 5 3/4"h. In nice condition.
Light stains on the Fan craze card but they go good together.
SOLD
Paypal OK, No extra fee
